hnk/index.html</a><br />\nViolent protests which began Friday stretched into the early hours of Saturday, beyond the midnight deadline when the new anti-mask regulations began. They spread out across the city and soon devolved into violent clashes, with protesters throwing petrol bombs and police responding with pepper spray and tear gas.<br />\n<br />\nUN rights chief :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hongkongfp.com/2019/10/06/un-rights-chief-troubled-alarmed-hong-kong-violence/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongfp.com%2F2019%2F10%2F06%2Fun-rights-chief-troubled-alarmed-hong-kong-violence%2F&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsL%2F3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=30e41f2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongfp.com/2019/10/06/un-rights-chief-troubled-alarmed-hong-kong-violence/</a><br />\nUN human rights chief Michelle Bachelet said Saturday she was &ldquo;troubled&rdquo; by Hong Kong&rsquo;s increasingly violent pro-democracy protests<br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Fm6HkAU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFm6HkAU.jpg&h=cfadcc90&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DNQQuuf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDNQQuuf.jpg&h=e8fe24d4&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dkz2kAV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdkz2kAV.jpg&h=e42958dd&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wt3FRHB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWt3FRHB.jpg&h=836cc635&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n<br />\n開始無人話警察武力不對等，國際開始支持港府。再係咁落去，美國人權及民主法案好可能被否決<br />\n<br />\n可唔可以做多D外國文宣 (Twitter), 唔好覺得有班人會做, 人人都要文宣!!"},{"pid":"cae9879c204e8db0cfe728447448a545dbd48458","tid":1631734,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:22:42.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"97c58e39d6246b9471bbddbc504b9db7db4174e3","tid":1631734,"uid":287494,"like":0,"dislik