rc=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n宜家回帶7月1日:佢哋(義士)唔走，我哋都唔會走！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/692795324506293?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F692795324506293%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsL%2F3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=370ea5c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/692795324506293?sfns=mo</a><br />\n\t<br />\n我哋點都唔會割 團結就是力量<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">香港人 反抗</span></span>"},{"pid":"56ec7d9854028705d5aa556ef5bf4620e11f20cb","tid":1631734,"uid":65074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:27:55.000Z","msg":"好多指責&amp;嗌交post<br />\n都係對家發起<br />\n依家我地連係網上討論都好被動<br />\n一直係防守位<br />\ntg d公海谷都差唔多情況<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真心懇求咁多連登仔upgrade下個腦<br />\n起碼load一load冇問題先upvote<br />\n嗌交post用不推文回覆或者唔理佢等佢沉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家要一齊向前行！"},{"pid":"286e4dc6db8408fa022a56ca788d2476d39d3e79","tid":1631734,"uid":33650,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d311e532d611ca062fce3c61e43992dda80aa7d0","tid":1631734,"uid":328352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:27:07.000Z","msg":"FB突然大量話連登公開割勇武蓆，fake?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:28:39.000Z","msg":"命運共同體 無諗過割"},{"pid":"430516ca6d46fed8e8884171f5f19862a910eb78","tid":1631734,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:30:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span sty